  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Stir in finely chopped onion and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes or until translucent.",
    "Toss in julienned bell pepper, halved cherry tomatoes, bay leaves, and paprika. Cook for another 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste.",
